#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kfind.appdata.xml:10
msgid "Find Files/Folders"
msgstr "Cerca Files/Dossieres"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kfind.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KFind can be used as a standalone search tool, launched by KRunner or from "
"your menu. It is also integrated into Dolphin as \"Open KFind\" in the "
"\"Tools\" menu. It allows you to find files by name, type or content."
msgstr ""
"KFind pote esser usate como singule instrumento de cerca, lanceate per "
"KRunner o ab tu menu. Anque il pote esser integrate in Dolphin como \"Aperi "
"KFind\" in le menu de \"Instrumentos\". Il te permitte trovar files per "
"nomine, typo o contento."

